RAD_LOVS.LOV_QUERY: Select Contract_ref_no,branch,contract_ccy,user_ref_no,module_code,latest_version_no,latest_event_seq_no from oltbs_contract a where branch = global.current_branch and contract_status = 'A' and (module_code = 'LB' and product_type in('L','C')) and exists (select 1 from olvw_avl_prod_br_usr where product_code =sypks_utils.get_product(A.CONTRACT_REF_NO) and branch_code = global.current_branch and user_id = global.user_id)

Select ccy_code, ccy_name from (select vw.ccy_code, ccy.ccy_name from olvws_product_currencies vw, cytms_ccy_defn ccy where vw.ccy_code = ccy.ccy_code and vw.product_code = sypks_utils.get_product(?) and ccy.record_stat = 'O' and ccy.auth_stat = 'A' and exists(select 1 from oltbs_contract where contract_ref_no = ? and module_code='LB' and product_type='C') union all SELECT DISTINCT c.CCY_CODE, c.CCY_NAME FROM cytms_ccy_defn C,LBTBS_BORROWER_CCY L where c.ccy_code=l.ccy AND l.contract_ref_no = ? and exists (select 1 from oltbs_contract where contract_ref_no = l.contract_ref_no and module_code='LB' and product_type='L')) where exists(select 1 from olvw_avl_prod_br_usr where product_code = ? and branch_code = global.current_branch and user_id = global.user_id)

SELECT SSI_MNEMONIC, SETTLEMENT_SEQ_NO SEQ_NO, BRANCH, PAY_ACCOUNT, RECV_ACCOUNT, COUNTERPARTY AGENT, CURRENCY FROM OLTMS_INSTR WHERE COUNTERPARTY IN (?, 'ALL') AND DECODE(BRANCH, 'ALL', ?, BRANCH) = ? AND DECODE(MODULE, 'AL', 'LB', MODULE) = 'LB' AND DECODE(CURRENCY, '*.*', ?, CURRENCY) = ? AND DECODE(PRODUCT_CODE, 'ALL', ?, PRODUCT_CODE) = ? AND RECORD_STAT = 'O' AND AUTH_STAT = 'A' AND EXISTS (SELECT * FROM olvws_PROD_ACNT_Access X WHERE (PAY_ACCOUNT = X.AC_GL_NO or RECV_ACCOUNT = X.AC_GL_NO) AND X.PRODUCT_CODE = ?)

select b.entity,b.entity_name,b.entity_type, b.PHONE_NO, b.FAX_NO, b.EMAIL from oltms_customer_entity a, oltms_customer_entity_details b where b.customer_no = a.customer_no and a.record_stat = 'O' and a.auth_stat = 'A' AND a.customer_no = ? union all select a.entity_id, b.entity_name, b.entity_type, b.PHONE_NO, b.FAX_NO, b.EMAIL from oltbs_contract_entity a,oltms_customer_entity_details b where contract_ref_no = decode(?,'TR',?,'DR',?,?) and event_seq_no = (select max(event_seq_no) from oltbs_contract_entity where contract_ref_no = decode(?,'TR',?,'DR',?,?) and contract_type = decode(?,'TR','FC','DR','TR') and drawdown_no = decode(?,'DR','0',?)) and contract_type = decode(?,'TR','FC','DR','TR') and drawdown_no = decode(?,'DR','0',?) and a.customer_no = ? and b.customer_no = a.customer_no and b.entity = a.entity_id and ? IN ('DR','TR','FC')
SELECT customer_no,customer_name1 FROM oltms_customer where record_stat = 'O' and auth_stat = 'A'

select a.customer_no customer_no ,a.customer_name1 customer_name1 from oltms_customer a, (select customer_no customer_no FROM oltms_customer UNION SELECT POSITION_IDENTIFIER customer_no FROM tlTMS_POSITION_IDENTIFIER) b where a.customer_no = b.customer_no

select a.customer_no customer_no ,a.customer_name1 customer_name1 from oltms_customer a, (select customer_no customer_no FROM oltms_customer UNION SELECT POSITION_IDENTIFIER customer_no FROM tlTMS_POSITION_IDENTIFIER) b where a.customer_no = b.customer_no

select a.participant, c.customer_name1 from lbtws_contract_participant a, oltms_customer c where a.contract_ref_no = ? and a.entry_seq_no = (select max(entry_seq_no) from lbtws_contract_participant where contract_ref_no = ?) and c.customer_no = a.participant and ((a.participant <> NVL(?,'*')) and (a.participant <> NVL(?,'*')))
select a.participant,b.customer_name1 from lbtbs_contract_participant a,oltm_customer b where a.participant = b.customer_no

RAD_GLOBAL_LOVS.LOV_QUERY: SELECT * FROM ((SELECT 'D' default_liab, l.Line_Code || l.Line_Serial Linkage_Ref_No, 'F' Linkage_Type, (SELECT Liab_No FROM Getm_Liab WHERE Id = l.Liab_Id) Liab_No, cust.CUSTOMER_NO Customer_No, l.Brn Branch, l.Line_Currency Currency, l.Description, l.Line_Expiry_Date Expiry_Date FROM Getm_Facility l, Getm_Liab_Cust cust WHERE l.Record_Stat = 'O' AND l.Liab_Id = cust.Liab_Id AND l.Once_Auth = 'Y' AND l.Availability_Flag = 'Y' AND (l.Line_Currency = ? OR Nvl(l.Ccy_Restriction, 'N') = 'N') AND (l.Id, NVL(?, ?)) IN (SELECT b.Id, a.Customer_No FROM Getm_Facility_Cust_Rest a, Getm_Facility b WHERE b.Customer_Rest_Type = 'A' AND a.Facility_Id = b.Id UNION (SELECT b.Id, c.Customer_No FROM Elvw_Customer c, Getm_Facility b WHERE b.Customer_Rest_Type = 'D' AND c.Record_Stat = 'O' AND c.Auth_Stat = 'A' MINUS SELECT Facility_Id, Customer_No FROM Getm_Facility_Cust_Rest)) AND (l.Id, ?) IN (SELECT b.Id, a.Product_Code FROM Getm_Facility_Prod_Rest a, Getm_Facility b WHERE b.Product_Rest_Type = 'A' AND a.Facility_Id = b.Id UNION (SELECT b.Id, c.Product_Code FROM Eltm_Product c, Getm_Facility b WHERE Product_Rest_Type = 'D' AND c.Record_Stat = 'O' AND c.Once_Auth = 'Y' MINUS SELECT Facility_Id, Product_Code FROM Getm_Facility_Prod_Rest)) AND (l.Id, ?) IN (SELECT b.Id, a.Branch_Code FROM Getm_Facility_Brn_Rest a, Getm_Facility b WHERE b.Branch_Rest_Type = 'A' AND a.Facility_Id = b.Id UNION (SELECT b.Id, a.Branch_Code FROM Eltm_Branch a, Getm_Facility b WHERE Branch_Rest_Type = 'D' AND a.Record_Stat = 'O' MINUS SELECT Facility_Id, Branch_Code FROM Getm_Facility_Brn_Rest)) AND (l.Id, ?) IN (SELECT b.Id, Ccy FROM Getm_Facility_Ccy_Rest a, Getm_Facility b WHERE b.Ccy_Rest_Type = 'A' AND a.Facility_Id = b.Id UNION (SELECT b.Id, Ccy_Code Ccy FROM Cytm_Ccy_Defn_Master c, Getm_Facility b WHERE b.Ccy_Rest_Type = 'D' AND c.Record_Stat = 'O' AND c.Auth_Stat = 'A' MINUS SELECT Facility_Id, Ccy FROM Getm_Facility_Ccy_Rest))) UNION (SELECT 'D' default_liab, Pp.Pool_Code Linkage_Ref_No, 'P' Linkage_Type, (SELECT Liab_No FROM Getm_Liab WHERE Id = Pp.Liab_Id) Liab_No, cust.Customer_No Customer_No, Pp.BRANCH_CODE Branch, Pool_Ccy Currency, Pp.Pool_Description, NULL Expiry_Date FROM Getm_Pool Pp, Getm_Liab_Cust cust WHERE Pp.Record_Stat = 'O' AND cust.Liab_Id = Pp.Liab_Id AND Pp.Once_Auth = 'Y') UNION (SELECT 'D' default_liab, c.Collateral_Code Linkage_Ref_No, 'T' Linkage_Type, Li.Liab_No Liab_No, cust.Customer_No Customer_No, c.Branch_Code Branch, c.Collateral_Currency Currency, c.Collateral_Description, c.End_Date Expiry_Date FROM Getm_Liab Li, Getm_Collat c, GETM_LIAB_CUST cust WHERE Li.Id = c.Liab_Id AND cust.Liab_Id = c.Liab_Id AND c.Available = 'Y' AND c.Record_Stat = 'O' AND c.Once_Auth = 'Y' UNION SELECT 'D' default_liab, c.Collateral_Code Linkage_Ref_No, 'T' Linkage_Type, (SELECT Liab_No FROM Getm_Liab WHERE Id = c.Liab_Id) Liab_No, cust.Customer_No Customer_No, c.Branch_Code Branch, c.Collateral_Currency Currency, c.Collateral_Description, c.End_Date Expiry_Date FROM Getm_Liab Li, Getm_Collat_Share s, Getm_Collat c, GETM_LIAB_CUST cust WHERE Li.Id = s.Liab_Id AND cust.Liab_Id = s.Liab_Id AND c.Id = s.Coll_Id AND c.Sharing_Req = 'Y' AND c.Available = 'Y' AND c.Record_Stat = 'O' AND c.Once_Auth = 'Y') UNION (SELECT 'D' default_liab, x.liab_no Linkage_Ref_No, 'L' Linkage_Type, x.liab_no Liab_No, y.customer_no Customer_No, x.liab_Branch Branch, x.liab_ccy Currency, x.liab_name description, NULL Expiry_Date FROM GETM_LIAB x, GETM_LIAB_CUST y WHERE x.id = y.liab_id AND x.record_stat = 'O' AND y.record_stat = 'O' AND x.Once_Auth = 'Y' AND y.Once_Auth = 'Y')) WHERE Customer_No = Nvl(?, ?) AND Linkage_Type = ? AND (('A' = ?) or ('S' = ? AND liab_no = ?) OR 'A' = ?)
